# Lab: Giau anh vao am thanh bang Inverse STFT va DWT.
# Muc tieu:
# 1. Tao file WAV PCM16 lam audio goc.
# 2. Tao file anh bi mat secret.png.
# 3. Sua doan ma Python de chi ra ten file audio va ten file anh.
# 4. Xu ly anh nhu spectrogram va dung Inverse STFT tao tin hieu mien thoi gian.
# 5. Dung DWT nhung tin hieu bi mat vao phan tan so cao va IDWT tao stego.wav.
# 6. Danh gia sai khac giua cover va stego.
